      "span_text": "To this end, consider a trained GTM-SD model: the projection of a tree x n on the topological map is obtained by mapping its root onto the lattice by using its hidden state assignment Q 1 . Several approaches exist to obtain such projection [CITATION_1] , again depending on the type of weighting given to the hidden states, as for the multisets encodings in Section III-B."
